    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="教学材料"><a href="#教学材料" class="headerlink" title="教学材料"></a>教学材料</h1><p>本节PPT和Geogebra不便上传，但<img src="/./1.png" alt="学案1"><img src="/./2.png" alt="学案2">可以上传，供大家交流使用。</p><h1 id="设计思路"><a href="#设计思路" class="headerlink" title="设计思路"></a>设计思路</h1><p>本节之前，学生已经学习了函数的概念和函数的基本性质（单调性和奇偶性）。本节就是在使用第三章所学知识，从定义域、值域、单调性、奇偶性、特殊值的角度，借助图象去总结规律，借助<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)=x,f(x)=x^2,f(x)=x^{-1},f(x)=x^3,f(x)=x^{\frac{1}{2}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" st